Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.02,OPED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}土を押し上げて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.68,OPED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}明日芽を出し
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.68,0:02:27.99,OPED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}やがて大きな花を咲かせる
