Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.62,0:01:15.12,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\3c&H595959&\bord1}明日之花們
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.61,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}知曉你的強大的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:25.39,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}人的希望  無名之人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.19,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}讚頌你的內心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.46,0:01:36.05,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}淡淡的小花們
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.38,0:01:41.19,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}堅韌不撓的藤蔓的形狀
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.85,0:01:46.61,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}懷中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.08,0:01:53.59,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自懷著不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.34,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.80,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命還在  就喊出願望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.11,0:02:08.30,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}心意終將貫穿星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.59,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}在漫長又短暫的時間的盡頭
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.14,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}你生存過的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.04,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}證據會
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.02,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}頂起土壤
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.68,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}明日發芽
